    Delete Tunnel on OVS
    KarafKeywords.Issue Command On Karaf Console    srm:recover INSTANCE ITM-TZ TZA
    BuiltIn.Wait Until Keyword Succeeds    60s    5s    Genius.Verify Tunnel Status as UP    TZA

